{
  "stem": "7094.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, sometimes, from best intention, people can overdo it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it's-- it's-- it's important, you know, that they-- they grow up normal.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They learn in it in an educational way without scarring, without damaging their thinking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's very difficult.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very difficult to-- to-- to lead a normal-- I never felt normal, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always felt-- and even now, I still have nightmares.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even now, when I come in a room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I avoided all the sort of big bar mitzvahs and big weddings, because whenever I come in a big room, I've got the image of the synagogue and the crowd there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's with me all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's-- it's-- it's difficult to fit in into a normal life to-- with my background.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found it difficult all along to pretend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is always this duality.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think-- until today, I thought I managed it much better.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But because maybe you are such a sympathetic listener, it's just one of those things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we come, and it touches this sore point which comes out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But normally, I couldn't have done it-- I haven't done it well today-- but I couldn't have done it years before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But now I thought that I'm-- I'm-- I might-- I've learned to live with it, that I can tell the story.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But yet, it's painful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it's-- it's full of sadness and pain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But at the same time, there is a lot of goodness, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, all the people in my life who helped me at one stage were good people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't want to believe-- to lose the belief in the goodness of man, because otherwise, again, life would be unbearable.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
